room_title: Escape room "Into the Future" by paradigmQ in Portland
room_address: 14415 SE Mill Plain Blvd #104B Vancouver, WA 98684
room_description: Its like nothing you’ve ever seen before.  It’s the future, but not as you expected it to be and not when you were just in your own time 127 years in the past.  Time and space have taken hold and transported you into another dimension it seems.  There must be a way to reverse it and set the space time continuum back to normal, but it will be tricky and must be done quickly or else…
